longBusinessSummary: Acast AB (publ) operates as a podcasting company in Europe, North America, and internationally. It operates a podcast platform to host and distribute their podcast. The company also offers podcast advertising services for promotion of the brand; and monetization opportunities for podcast creators and advertisers. Acast AB (publ) was incorporated in 2013 and is headquartered in Stockholm, Sweden.
